{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>政府在某山区修建了一条道路，恰好穿越总共$m$个村庄的每个村庄一次，没有回路或交叉，任意两个村庄只能通过这条路来往。已知任意两个相邻的村庄之间的距离为$d\\_i$(为正整数)，其中，$0 < i < m$。为了提高山区的文化素质，政府又决定从$m$个村中选择$n$个村建小学(设$0 < n ≤ m < 500$)。请根据给定的$m$、$n$以及所有相邻村庄的距离，选择在哪些村庄建小学，才使得所有村到最近小学的距离总和最小，计算最小值。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"山区建小学 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>各村庄到最近学校的距离之和的最小值。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第1行为$m$和$n$，其间用空格间隔<p><p>第2行为$m-1$ 个整数，依次表示从一端到另一端的相邻村庄的距离，整数之间以空格间隔。<p><p>例如:<p>","examples":"<input>10 3\n2 4 6 5 2 4 3 1 3\n</input><output>10 2\n3 1 3 1 1 1 1 1 3\n\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1197","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}